      "side": 1,
      "message": "maybeReload is called in Set and GetMulti, and if the connection dies and there are a lot of Set or Get calls, they will all be serialized on the h.clientMutex.Lock(). Not sure if that\u0027s an issue, but maybe just always spin up a background Go routine that checks for disconnects every 10s and tries to reconnect and avoid the serialization on the maybeReload() call.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 131,
        "startChar": 28,
